:: Public Holidays
"Liberation Day"                                        public on january 1
"Victory Day"                                           public on january 2
"International Workers Day"                             public on may 1
"Commemoration of the Assault on Cuartel Moncada"       public on july 25
"National Rebellion Day"                                public on july 26
"Commemoration of the Assault on Cuartel Moncada"       public on july 27
"Independence Day"                                      public on october 10
"End of the Year"                                       public on december 31

:: Religious
"Good Friday"                                           public religious easter minus 2
"Christmas"                                             public religious on december 25

